##About##

Systray widget used to load ICC color profiles with different color temperatures, either on demand
or automatically based on the sun's position.

iccloader's main inspiration is [redshift][1].

##Usage##

```sh
iccloader &
```

##Screenshots##

Screenshots using the Zukitwo GTK3 theme and Tango icons

##Known problems##

- "solpos" will stop working after 2050


[1]: http://jonls.dk/redshift/

